data.description: Discover your dream home situated on 5.8 acres of picturesque landscape. Tucked away from the road, this spacious home, offers privacy and a serene setting. Step onto the inviting front porch and enter into a light-filled open floor plan, adorned with brand new flooring and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. The primary bedroom boasts a generous walk-in closet, while the convenience of a main-level laundry room adds to the ease of living. Venture downstairs to find a spacious finished lower level offering versatility with a large family room, third bedroom, and bonus room. Enjoy the proximity to Fairway Shores Golf Course and Little Elk Lake, making this the ideal retreat for peaceful living and outdoor adventures.
